                                    <Label styleClass="header2" text="Our Vision" />
                                    <TextArea editable="false" prefHeight="350.0" prefWidth="1000.0" text="Neckfleck has a clear vision of combining nostalgia with modern convenience. As a small, locally run video rental shop, we have expanded our inventory to encompass a diverse range of items, including old movie records, DVDs, and video games. Recognizing the need to adapt to changing times, we have computerized our operations to offer a seamless rental experience for our customers.&#10;&#10;With our computer-based inventory system, customers can effortlessly explore our extensive collection and check the availability of their favorite movies, TV series, and games. Our focus on exceptional customer service ensures that our knowledgeable staff is always ready to provide personalized recommendations and assistance, fostering a warm and inviting environment.&#10;&#10;Our vision is to create a memorable and enjoyable experience for our customers, blending the nostalgia of the past with the convenience of modern technology. We take pride in offering a unique and comprehensive selection while maintaining a personalized touch that sets us apart. NeckFleck is committed to delivering top-notch customer service and being the go-to destination for all your movie and gaming needs.&#10;" wrapText="true" />
                                 </children>
